User
   ~email String
   ~password String Maybe
   ~verkey String Maybe
   ~verified Bool
   UniqueUser email
   deriving Typeable
Email
   ~email String
   ~userId UserId Maybe
   ~verkey String Maybe
   UniqueEmail email
Person
   ~email String
   UniquePerson email
   ~name String
   ~street String
   ~number Int
   deriving Show
Friends
   ~email String
   UniqueFriend email
   ~requests [String]
   ~friends [String]
   ~outgoingRequests [String]
